## ğŸ§  Getting Started

1. **Fork the Repository**
   - Click **Fork** at the top right of the [VisionLex repo](https://github.com/Zangetsu-Tensa/VisionLex-A-Multimodal-Text-Image-Understanding-Framework.git).

2. **Clone Your Fork**
```bash
